/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"【19:00】下午4時許，一名年約30歲男子於將軍澳景林邨景桃樓高層寓所墮下，倒卧大廈一樓平台。警方及消防接報到場，當場證實男子死亡，並把屍體由平台搬至後樓梯位置。現場消息指出，男子與父母和姊姊一家四口居住上址高層一單位，男子趁家人不為意時由家中客廳窗戶跳下。消息稱，死者近日失業鬱鬱不歡。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，接獲事主的父親報案，懷疑事主從高處墮下。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事主從上址一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自願賠錢走人然後因為失業自殺？"},{"pid":"1630ef7cdca638dbf5fe8ba7c14f4f4a344ab0ad","tid":1958251,"uid":174060,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sAEsb2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsAEsb2e.png&h=5ce804a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾時到呢件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSmVkVA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSmVkVA.png&h=b4082c34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e202d3ee77da855a63afb7ec6084a3d2866c04d2","tid":1958251,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d1d500baac6234e89ea3e2111c9c868c918571","tid":1958251,"uid":4632,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"特首辦<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新聞</span></span>主任呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"好似唔小野呢個位，唔係請開淫賤聯呢類人？"},{"pid":"cf83e6a1062c80b8721ab445973d169c8cf232f4","tid":1958251,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\